data.title: Privilege confirms SHINE Ibiza, Trance residency by Paul van Dyk
data.meta_description: Privilege confirms SHINE Ibiza, Trance residency by Paul van Dyk
data.text:
SHINE Ibiza makes its debut in Privilege Ibiza with a 12-week residency kicking off on July 9th.

SHINE Ibiza is probably the most authentic Trance night in Ibiza with a massive lineup leaded each week by Paul van Dyk and joined by huge artists such as Aly & Fila, Ben Nicky and Bryan Kearney across the summer.

Of the move, legendary DJ and long-time Ibiza club-resident Paul van Dyk says: “what SHINE offers, is a world of opportunities - a hub to an international community and a place where we belong no matter where we’re from. The trance family is a global collective of positive, caring and fun-loving people. Myself, my fellow DJs, the event organizers and club staff will go the extra mile to provide the best possible experience for them. I look forward, with the greatest anticipation to seeing you at SHINE!”.

SHINE residents Aly & Fila added “We are very much looking forward to being part of SHINE Ibiza this summer. It is great to see this dedicated Trance event on the White Isle. See you several times over the summer!”

The brand new party at Privilege that will bring the best atmosphere and music from July 9th till September 17th, will take place at Vista, the club located at the Privilege terrace with the most breathtaking views of Old Ibiza Town. With no doubts, the perfect location to dance all night long till sunrise.

Get your tickets for SHINE Ibiza, every Monday from July 9th till September 17th at Privilege Ibiza 2018!
